The paper deals with deep learning for image restoration, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of synthesized paired data to train the deep convolutional neural network (DCNN), which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the generalization error in statistical learning, which is a topic in both machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also deals with image and multimedia processing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it discusses the performance of the DCNN on real-world data.
